text:
It is a precinct of the Ang Mo Kio GRC.It has a foodcentre call Teck Ghee Court Foodcentre and Market and also lots of other amenities around.Easily reachable by public buses, taxis and own transports.The main roads here are Ang Mo Kio Ave 8, Street 31& Street 32.Parking is available at HDB car parks around.

Dated : 22/10/2018 ( Monday ).
